                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-895" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM KEEDING</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 89.) I produce two sixpences,</p>
               <p>which I got from Mrs. Crosby—I searched the prisoner, and found on him 4jrf. in copper money.</p>
